            	Your rights of access and correction<br>
            	The accuracy of your personal information is important. Meet The People takes reasonable steps to ensure personal information it holds about you is accurate, complete, up-to-date, relevant and not misleading. If you believe that any personal information Meet The People holds about you is incorrect, please contact us meetthepeople@gmail.com.<br>
